14 WHEREAS, additional charter school seats are needed to serve the 21,000 students who
15 currently appear on charter school wait lists in Georgia.
16 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
17 the members of this body recognize February 26, 2025, as Charter Schools Day at the state
18 capitol.
19 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
20 and directed to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the
21 Georgia Charter Schools Association, the public, and the press.
